在全世界大多数国家的足球界中都或多或少的存在着针对同性恋的歧视现象。有人认为同性恋仍然是职业足球的禁忌<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4426278.stm|title=Is homophobia in football still a taboo?|accessdate=12 August 2009|date=10 November 2005|author=Matt Williams|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2005-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051205141959/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/4426278.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，并且会持续下去<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/columnists/simon_barnes/article662923.ece|title=Football destined to remain the last bastion of homophobia - that's the straight, naked truth|accessdate=12 August 2009|date=6 October 2006|author=Simon Barnes|publisher=''The Times'' | location=London}}</ref>。

